name: 2021 a Space Odyssey
description:
"2021 a Space Odyssey" - By Bryant W

Humanity finds a mysterious, obviously artificial object buried beneath the Lunar surface and, within it lies a "window" in which some kind of pattern emerges that if unlocked can change humanities fundamental grasp on reality.

Enjoy the future!

This artwork was created using old illustrations dating back in the early 1930's collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in photoshop.

5120px x 5120px .jpg - Date of completion 11/21/2021
